Project goal is to facilitate users to access built-in webcams or connected USB webcams directly from web page.
No Need to register or copy any DLL's at user side. It's a web based  i.e. Java Applet web embedded.
user is able to capture, crop and save images from a live streaming to pc or to the specified server.

You need to run MyAppletLauncher.java class for executing the project or
Just Export this myeclipse code as a Jar, Sign it and embed it in a web page as Java Applet invoking MyAppletLauncher.java class.